.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, architect, photographer, manager
House: farmhouse, townhouse, craftsman, cottage
1. the manager is on the right of the photographer##1
2. the craftsman house is between the cottage house and the photographer##2
3. the farmhouse house is between the craftsman house and the entrepreneur##2
4. the cottage house is on the far right##1
5. the architect is on the left or right of the manager##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Job    | entrepreneur | photographer | manager | architect |
| House   | townhouse | farmhouse  | craftsman    | cottage  |

