.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, chinchilla, fish, lizard
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, orange, turquise, coral
1. the person who likes coral is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
4. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the lizard##2
5. the person who likes orange is the person who likes orange##1
6. the person who likes orange is between the person who likes turquise and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Pet   | ferret | lizard | fish | chinchilla     |
| Color     | amber | coral  | orange   | turquise |

