.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
House: wooden, cottage, tower, futuristic
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, subway, trike
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the futuristic house is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the futuristic house is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
4. the futuristic house is on the left of the tower house##1
5. the wooden house is on the left of the cottage house##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| House         | futuristic | tower | wooden | cottage   |
| Transport   | helicopter | subway | bike      | trike |

