.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, bellflower, iris, zinnia
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, dubstep, techno, disco
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
3. the fan of disco is the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who growsbellflower is between the fan of dubstep and the fan of gospel##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Flower     | tulip | bellflower   | iris      | zinnia      |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep     | techno | gospel | disco |

