.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
House: colonial, wooden, farmhouse, futuristic
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, blood-red, light-blue, purple
1. the wooden house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
2. the wooden house is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person who likes purple is the farmhouse house##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
5. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| House       | colonial | farmhouse | futuristic    | wooden      |
| Color   | light-blue       | purple       | blood-red | coral |

