.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, fisherman, freelancer, musician
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, surfing, cricket, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the nurse##1
4. the nurse is on the far left##1
5. the freelancer is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Job   | nurse     | fisherman  | musician | freelancer |
| Sport     | parkour | skateboarding | surfing     | cricket    |

