1. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
5. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Flower   | bellflower | azalea  | rose | lily |
