.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, weightlifting, badminton, water-polo
City: miami, hamburg, marseilles, liverpool
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Sport   | weightlifting  | skiing | water-polo  | badminton      |
| City    | liverpool | miami | marseilles | hamburg |

