.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, carrot, broccoli, apple
City: rome, liverpool, hamburg, paris
1. the person eating peas is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the person eating carrot is the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is the person eating broccoli##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
6. the person traveling to hamburg is the person eating peas##1
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Food         | carrot | apple | broccoli | peas |
| City   | paris     | rome       | liverpool   | hamburg      |

