.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-16::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, videographer, firefighter, paramedic
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, game, oliveros, bongani
1. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
2. the paramedic is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
3. the electrician is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
4. the paramedic is on the left of the firefighter##1
5. the swisher-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Job   | electrician | paramedic | firefighter | videographer |
| Cigar         | game  | oliveros   | bongani | swisher     |

