.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, tomato, pear, mango
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, grey, yellow, green
1. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating mango##1
2. the person who likes green is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
4. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
5. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Food      | zucchini | tomato    | mango  | pear |
| Color   | amber       | grey | yellow | green  |

