.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-18::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, lettuce, watermelon, peas
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, green, lavender, yellow
1. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
2. the person eating lettuce is the person who likes yellow##1
3. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
4. the person eating peas is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who likes lavender is between the person eating peas and the person who likes yellow##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Food   | watermelon | lettuce  | pineapple  | peas |
| Color           | brown    | yellow | lavender | green |

