There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, coral, mauve, green
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
3. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports        | action       | disaster   | epic |
| Color    | green | mauve | coral | chestnut  |

