.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, coach, freelancer, project-manager
City: paris, prague, london, colone
1. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to colone is the person traveling to colone##1
3. the project-manager is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
4. the person traveling to paris is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
6. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the pilot##1
7. the freelancer is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Job   | coach     | pilot     | freelancer          | project-manager |
| City      | paris | prague | colone | london  |

 